@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080/api/travel
@token = your_jwt_token_here

### Health (no token)
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### List travel plans
GET {{baseUrl}}/travel-plans
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Create travel plan
POST {{baseUrl}}/travel-plans
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Leto u Grckoj",
  "description": "Odmor na Kritu",
  "startDate": "2026-07-01",
  "endDate": "2026-07-14",
  "plannedBudget": 1500,
  "notes": "Rezervisati let"
}

### Add destination
POST {{baseUrl}}/travel-plans/1/destinations
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Heraklion",
  "location": "Kreta, Grcka",
  "arrivalDate": "2026-07-01",
  "departureDate": "2026-07-07",
  "description": "Prva destinacija"
}
